com.gexin.rp.sdk.base.ITemplate
public class LinkTemplate
extends com.gexin.rp.sdk.template.AbstractTemplate

在通知栏显示一条含图标、标题等的通知，用户点击可打开您指定的网页。
For this template, a notification with icon and title will appear in the notification area. Go to the specific web page after clicking the notification.
